Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:18.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状況は非科学的に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情のモンタージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰が誰を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:30.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けば　逃げてく視線　感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:33.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気のせいじゃつれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.49,0:24:38.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}アンテナは才能って言うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:42.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だってだって　知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:44.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:50.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}青春の温度差　今のうち　正してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:55.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明日解決するなら　今でもよくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:25:01.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君のミステリー　解いてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:05.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}少年の秘密めいた背中探せ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:09.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日も君はファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:13.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惹けれてゆくよ　ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:19.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨らんだ好奇心　トリックはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:23.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気になるよ　興味深い
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.46,0:25:25.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:18.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狀況完全不科學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情如拼貼畫般交織
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是誰在將誰呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:30.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}回頭時感覺到你逃避的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:33.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}說這是錯覺未免無情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.49,0:24:38.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直覺該稱為才能才對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:42.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我想瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:44.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}難道你並非如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:50.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}現在就為你糾正青春的溫差
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:55.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}既然明天能解決 不如趁現在搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:25:01.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要解開你的懸疑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:05.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}探尋少年神秘的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:09.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天的你也如同幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:13.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狡猾地吸引著我不斷沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:19.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨脹的好奇中分明不含心機
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:23.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人在意 耐人尋味
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.46,0:25:25.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這究竟是為什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到嗎 那本「傍晚便成骸」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是暑假的時候帶回鄉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.66,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：摩耶花COS的是赤塚不二夫「甜蜜小天使」中的主角加賀美厚子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.49,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：河內COS的是KOF系列的金
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那你就幫著畫海報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海報…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 要萌的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐…把漫畫的名字記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:24.66,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(1212,880)}Wild Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同學 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了料理競賽是十一點半開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在漫研畫海報才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那麼把摩耶花排在最後出場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你十二點十分到就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我會想辦法的 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我也得到總務委員會去露個臉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他倒是很享受KANYA祭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個搬到體育館去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 學長你不去到處逛逛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做的雜事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是都稍微看過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼有趣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 聽說圍棋部出現了怪盜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷走了棋子 還留下了犯罪聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是嗎 圍棋部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 不過我覺得只是部員自導自演而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我聽岡野說無伴奏合唱部也出了類似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 冷飲箱裡的一瓶飲料被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有犯罪聲明？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說裡面裝著一張奇怪的便條
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下可好玩起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 福部 笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我一定會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你願意幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等賣出去了再謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 定價和數量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一本200日元 數量有…200本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下錯訂單所以印多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想儘量多賣一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降到150日元 給我20本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們的小冊子一起以200元的價格捆綁銷售
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是做什麼 給我一本樣書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後帶上實物去找人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換一個求助方式 效果就會大有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入須學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入須學姐很擅長拜託別人做事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請教我一招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論要拜託什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要引導對方主動行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此 就必須讓對方身心都感到滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體方法有很多 不過你能用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是讓對方覺得他肩負著你的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓對方覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能做到這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後對方就很容易竭盡全力來幫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竭盡全力來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也不要把問題說得太嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說得太嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓對方覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他而言只是舉手之勞的事 對你而言卻很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是在沒人的地方 找異性幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把文集拿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trick or Treat？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.79,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：孩子們在萬聖節討要點心時必說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點心研究會的訪問銷售
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來袋餅乾怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一袋100日元喲 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著這個去賣東西好像不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用兩袋餅乾跟你們換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在買文集附送那把手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再送你這個 當作南瓜給你的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(873,204)}超速度!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(786,348)}海報繪製大比拼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(708,528)}漫畫研究會引以為傲的畫手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz274.477\fn@FZLiBian-S02\fs45\c&H718886&\3c&HDBEAEB&\b1\pos(589.5,517.5)}魔女VS女豹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫研究會引以為傲的畫手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還在忙著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信摩耶花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 福部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們隊的須原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是酒家的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那還挺厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好加油吧 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「好好」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 本次眾所矚目的參賽隊伍有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一隊 好滋味隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二隊 摩根勒菲隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.10,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：Fata Morgana 亞瑟王傳奇中登場的女巫 也有海市蜃樓的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三隊 天文部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及四隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊以三人為一組 每人限時20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20分過後換下一位隊員上場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一人做菜時其他人不得插嘴 否則視為犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做福部流海鮮炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米飯得從淘米蒸飯做起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 福部同學就要做壓軸的大將了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我打頭陣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然做不了海鮮炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第幾個出場都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊每人做一道菜以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食材在中央的檯子上 先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果食材用完了 允許從校內補充
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 打頭陣的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Own your kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs52.5}請各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.00,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}秋 分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.00,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}晝夜等長日 乃是秋分時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 Wild Fire料理競賽開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊將會為我們帶來什麼樣的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 古典部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在將魚乾的頭部和內臟一一摘除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是精細的手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長 你覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先處理是很重要的 副部長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根勒菲隊準備了蛤仔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要做白蘿蔔醬湯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 福部同學 那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒削蘿蔔皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提示是犯規的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮 皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 要一塊塊削嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水在沸騰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊 這樣好像要花很多時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在莫比烏斯環之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.69,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：出自「機動戰士高達 逆襲的夏亞」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊要做什麼現在還不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 古典部隊好像犯難了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是肉湯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 好滋味隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是經典中的經典 肉醬汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照這個速度會趕不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先鋒選手們 時間就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Change Element
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs52.5}換  人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：出自「創聖的大天使」 其中的Vector Machine可更換駕駛員(即Change Element)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 只做了一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 千反田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊主力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常精彩的刀工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是白蘿蔔的真正姿態 太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為是皮 現在污染的河流好像都要被淨化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:37.42,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：「河」與「皮」在日語中同音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了 已經做好一道菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然要有千反田同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 古典部居然用拜神式淘米法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且毫不可惜地把僅有6升的水倒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為米的美味下了必死的決心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 天文部隊主力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊 是什麼料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過激fire
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.07,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：「超時空要塞7」中熱氣·巴薩拉常說的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面 古典部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是擬似豆腐燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.66,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：豆腐搗碎加各種材料使其看上去像是蛋或其他菜的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故鄉的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裕美！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.54,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：杉田智和的朋友的媽媽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擬似豆腐燒什麼的聽都沒聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 摩根勒菲隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照燒鰤魚正漸入佳境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Brilliant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs52.5}太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.34,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：「女神異聞錄3」中桐條美鶴常說的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部的擬似豆腐燒做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著肚子都餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位主力究竟是何許人也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪農地主千反田家長女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田愛琉大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來看看天文部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的前衛派料理還在進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被黑暗吞噬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.40,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：杉田智和在「蒼翼默示錄」中所配角色的招式之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把煮好的土豆和片栗粉一起放進了研缽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次要做薯餅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部很熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 這下子不妙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙？什麼不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊 提示是犯規的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 她沒理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此已經過去了40分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請換大將上場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厲害啊 千反田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道你這麼會做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 了不起了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有食材了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 終於進入大將戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好滋味隊準備了蘋果作為甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸地雕出兔子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部的大將還沒出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 好滋味隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了兔子之外 還開始雕花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好滋味隊無視大將還沒現身的古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備起甜點來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！賽場跑進了一個穿便裝的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是古典部隊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她來得及嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊的大將 終於登場了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 古典部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一波方平一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食材已經用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果什麼都做不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大將戰自然只能得鴨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路奮戰到現在的古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能止步於此了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊 拿下了小號洋蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是靠這麼個小洋蔥能做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大將似乎沒有主意 只是站在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢 古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一道菜也做不出來的話可是要出局的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算拿那麼點食材怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都要怪誰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部大將 束手無策！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.70,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：「夜航」 安托萬·德·聖-埃克絮佩里出版於1931年的小說 法國著名文學獎費米娜獎獲獎作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完工了 摩根勒菲隊的蛋包飯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想 快想想！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊要在此倒下了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該 應該能做些什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊 無計可施！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的時間只有十分鐘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能就此等待時間用盡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:54.78,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學 剛才是不是有人叫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:01.95,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.37,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文部隊 把香蕉用來煮醬汁了！香…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.38,UP_Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動室那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志 過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到正下面來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊 先鋒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！意想不到的超展開！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那難道是麵粉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有違反規則 那就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.45,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：後半句原出自「蒼天航路」中曹操的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下七分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild Fire料理競賽 各隊進入收尾階段時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊終於行動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這極端不利的環境下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們究竟會如何奮戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們竟然把甜蝦的頭取出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鮮什錦炸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海鮮什錦炸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:21:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild Fire料理競賽 倒計時五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 料理研 至少也要準備好圓勺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圓勺 圓勺 對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了圓勺的古典部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於開始進行下一步工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 古典部隊 正以怒濤之勢展開反擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海鮮什錦炸蓋飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊 他們來得及嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一分鐘！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撈起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往上放蘿蔔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 現在宣佈結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲勝的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒炸透
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間不夠又別無選擇的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到這樣已經很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒有圓勺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有圓勺就能做得很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿那個居然花了一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也夠笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然沒有就該想沒有的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 實在非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明認真確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該最後再檢查一遍的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也一開始就覺得奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我應該確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先離開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪聲明…！
